655
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,280
Cringe.

656
00:34:21,199 --> 00:34:22,039
He has no clue about
my pen name.

657
00:34:23,440 --> 00:34:24,320
He'd have no idea

658
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:25,440
