664
00:34:34,960 --> 00:34:35,719
Thank you all so much for today.
Thank you, thank you!

665
00:34:36,679 --> 00:34:37,119
Xiaofei,
- Lead the way.
- Thank you!
Sure!

666
00:34:38,519 --> 00:34:39,360
This way, everyone!
Let's pick up your drinks.

667
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:41,360
Thanks! Bye!

668
00:34:50,920 --> 00:34:51,480
Shican,

669
