693
00:37:21,199 --> 00:37:22,000
No, I...

694
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,159
- That was just...
- Okay, look.

695
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:25,280
Nobody knows you better than I do.

696
00:37:25,719 --> 00:37:26,800
