748
00:40:19,119 --> 00:40:20,000
"The exposure"

749
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:21,199
"wasn't me or my lawyers."

750
00:40:32,599 --> 00:40:33,400
Can't rule out retaliation

751
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:34,440
