With public security as solid as it is,

757
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:46,559
there's no way Cen Sisi is able

758
00:40:47,719 --> 00:40:48,440
to pull off

759
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:49,559
anything too drastic.

760
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:58,840
"An incredible legend."

761
00:41:00,039 --> 00:41:00,800
"SG,"

762
