803
00:44:14,880 --> 00:44:15,280
Good girl.

804
00:44:16,119 --> 00:44:16,920
Stay with me a little longer.

805
00:44:17,880 --> 00:44:18,400
I promise

806
00:44:18,639 --> 00:44:19,960
